  "title": "fix(Configure): update was not apply when trigger onSearchStateChange",
  "body": "The previous fix was triggering the onSearchStateChange hooks with the wrong information because the update was not yet performed.\r\n\r\nUltimately we want to:\r\n1. call refine + transitionState when new props are passed to our component. \r\n2. call refine + transition when a component did mount. ",
